  "instructions": "# x402 Data Bazaar\\n\\nReal-world data APIs for AI and agentic workflows. Pay per request with USDC on Base.\\n\\n## Core Legacy Endpoints\\n- VIN decode, weather decision briefs, FX conversion, holidays/business days, IP geolocation, nutrition, FDA recalls/adverse events, census population, BLS CPI/unemployment, AQI, congress bills.\\n\\n## Expanded Endpoint Families\\n- Finance: stock quotes/search/candles, treasury rates, fed funds rate, yield curve, credit spreads, real rates, inflation expectations.\\n- Government & Macro: BLS jobs/wages/PCE, census housing/income/age.\\n- FDA: drug labels, device events/recalls, NDC lookups, path alias for drug events.\\n- Weather: historical, alerts, marine, UV, AQI alias route, extremes and freeze-risk analytics.\\n- Location: geocode, reverse geocode, timezone, zipcode, elevation.\\n- Domain Intelligence: whois/rdap, dns, ssl cert, domain availability.\\n- Legal/Regulatory: SEC filings/company facts/insider trades, sanctions, court cases/opinions/citations/court-info/clusters.\\n- Sports: scores, standings, schedules, odds.\\n- World Data: World Bank indicators, country profiles.\\n\\n## Payment\\nUSDC on Base via x402 v2. Paid endpoints return 402 with machine-readable payment requirements until settled.\\n\\n## Discovery\\nUse GET /api for machine-readable catalog entries, canonical example URLs, pricing metadata, and route-level payment specs."
